    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p>Nomo FOMO helps connect people online so that they can meet up offline, where the real magic happens.  We help you avoid missed meet up opportunities of getting FOMO (fear of missing out) on an amazing trip or business networking connection while also helping make all aspects of travel as easy and convenient as possible.</p>
    <p>We believe that no matter what the purpose of your trip is, we want to give you the tools to be engaged with your network and be as private or public about your travels as possible.  This is why we focus on travel and only travel.  Here it is about helping spark that creativity around the next trip whether it is figuring out how to maximize your next business trip so you can spend less time on the road per year or planning a dream trip based off of other people's past iteneraries, either way we give you the encouragement and tools to make it possible.</p>
